---
// HELPERS
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

// IMAGES
import problemIllo from "@/assets/problem-illustration.png";
---

<section id="problem" class="sec-pad">
  <div class="container container-md">
    <span class="eyebrow" data-reveal><span class="num">// 01</span> The problem</span>
    <p class="statement" data-fill-words>
      Most local business websites look like they were built in an afternoon. Because honestly, a lot
      of them were.
    </p>

    <div class="prob-grid">
      <div class="prob-copy" data-reveal>
        <p>
          GoDaddy Airo. Wix. A template someone threw together real quick. They look fine at first
          glance, but they load slow, they don't rank on Google, and they don't make your business
          look like the best option in town.
        </p>
        <p>
          A huge number of local businesses either don't have a website at all, or have one so outdated
          it's doing more harm than good. A brand-new, well-built site immediately puts you ahead of
          most of your competition before the phone even rings.
        </p>
        <p class="strong">
          That's the difference between winning the job and losing it to whoever shows up better
          online.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="prob-illo" data-reveal>
        <Image src={problemIllo} alt="A slow, templated competitor website" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  .statement {
    max-width: 21ch;
    margin: var(--_spacing---space--7) 0 0;
    font: 700 clamp(2.2rem, 4.6vw, 4.4rem)/1.08 var(--font-display);
    letter-spacing: var(--track-tight);
  }
  .prob-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
    gap: var(--_spacing---section-space--main);
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: var(--_spacing---section-space--large);
  }
  .prob-copy p {
    max-width: 56ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--_spacing---space--6);
    font: 400 1.0625rem/1.6 var(--font-body);
    color: var(--fg2);
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .prob-copy p.strong {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--fg1);
  }
  .prob-illo {
    line-height: 0;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 26px 46px rgba(20, 30, 15, 0.13));
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .prob-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
